改列作阻礙警務人員執行職務，3名被捕青年涉嫌阻礙警務人員執行職務被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨零時許，東九龍衝鋒隊在九龍城巡邏，其間見5名青年聚集在賈炳達道與打鼓嶺道交界，於是上前截查。惟5人拔足逃跑，警員追入附近城南道後巷截獲其中3人，另外兩人逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，調查期間14歲姓歐青年突然企圖搶警槍，但被其他在場警員制服。事件中，一名軍裝警長及一名便裝警員受傷，他們由接報救護員送院治理。被捕3人分別姓羅13歲、姓歐及姓王14歲，他們是朋友關係。歐涉嫌企圖搶劫及阻差辦公，另外兩人同涉阻差辦公被捕，案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，羅與歐是黃大仙區一間學校的中二學生，王是區內一間小學六年級生。警方正了解他們在上址留連的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201221/USRSOCHSZJB4LOBKU7DXNKCFDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201221%2FUSRSOCHSZJB4LOBKU7DXNKCFDY%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=040cb8e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201221%2FUSRSOCHSZJB4LOBKU7DXNKCFDY%2F&h=d1481834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201221/USRSOCHSZJB4LOBKU7DXNKCFDY/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"老屈唔使本 同公安一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92de0452574aaafe7160b4c7d52eb1e9414b473","tid":2335040,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4756d05a5f7a64964ab34aa720afc78ae2067396","tid":2335040,"uid":144541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"吹咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQGS67w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3